WEBVTT

00:00.024 --> 00:01.964
Previously on Genius...

00:01.964 --> 00:03.132
Move in with me.

00:03.133 --> 00:05.935
Think how wonderful it would be.

00:09.273 --> 00:11.643
This is Géry Pieret.

00:11.644 --> 00:14.046
Consider these a
token of our new friendship.

00:14.047 --> 00:16.242
You stole them, from the Louvre?

00:16.242 --> 00:17.510
I liberated them.

00:17.511 --> 00:19.412
But there is a
small delivery fee.

00:19.413 --> 00:20.813
50 francs.

00:20.814 --> 00:22.181
Opium.

00:22.182 --> 00:24.230
Have you tried it?
I want to make you happy.

00:24.231 --> 00:25.431
At least for a little while.

00:25.432 --> 00:26.966
I am not your prisoner.

00:26.967 --> 00:28.167
I made a mistake.

00:28.168 --> 00:29.502
I don't know what I
would do if I lost you.

00:29.503 --> 00:34.039
Pablo Picasso,
meet Henri Matisse.

00:34.040 --> 00:37.510
I see you've already
met, uh, Monsieur Braque.

00:37.511 --> 00:39.545
He is the youngest of the
Wild Beasts, as they call us.

00:39.546 --> 00:41.347
What do you want?

00:41.348 --> 00:43.048
You haven't surfaced in months.

00:43.049 --> 00:44.583
Why do you care, Braque?

00:44.584 --> 00:45.951
We barely know each other.

00:45.952 --> 00:47.219
I would like to change that.

00:47.220 --> 00:48.621
I really do admire your work.

00:48.622 --> 00:50.556
Oh, it's ghastly, Pablo.

00:50.557 --> 00:54.059
That is the most astute art
critique you have ever given, Gertrude.

00:54.327 --> 00:55.761
Congratulations.

00:55.762 --> 00:58.730
You said you wanted to
offend, you've done it.

